      h4 Growing spinner
      p If you don't fancy a border spinner, switch to the grow spinner. While it doesn't technically spin, it does repeatedly grow!

      .bd-example
        .spinner-grow(role='status')
          span.visually-hidden Loading...

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="spinner-grow" role="status"&gt;
          |   &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

