      h4 Alignment
      p Spinners in Bootstrap are built with <code>rem</code>s, <code>currentColor</code>, and <code>display: inline-flex</code>. This means they can easily be resized, recolored, and quickly aligned.

      h4 Margin
      p Use margin utilities like <code>.m-5</code> for easy spacing.

      .bd-example
        .spinner-border.m-5(role='status')
          span.visually-hidden Loading...

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="spinner-border m-5" role="status"&gt;
          |   &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      h4 Placement
      p Use flexbox utilities, float utilities, or text alignment utilities to place spinners exactly where you need them in any situation.

      h4 Flex

      .bd-example
        .d-flex.justify-content-center
          .spinner-border(role='status')
            span.visually-hidden Loading...

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="d-flex justify-content-center"&gt;
          |   &lt;div class="spinner-border" role="status"&gt;
          |     &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          |   &lt;/div&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      .bd-example
        .d-flex.align-items-center
          strong(role='status') Loading...
          .spinner-border.ms-auto(aria-hidden='true')

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="d-flex align-items-center"&gt;
          |   &lt;strong role="status"&gt;Loading...&lt;/strong&gt;
          |   &lt;div class="spinner-border ms-auto" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      h4 Floats

      .bd-example
        .clearfix
          .spinner-border.float-end(role='status')
            span.visually-hidden Loading...

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="clearfix"&gt;
