          |     &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          |   &lt;/div&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      h4 Size
      p Add <code>.spinner-border-sm</code> and <code>.spinner-grow-sm</code> to make a smaller spinner that can quickly be used within other components.

      .bd-example
        .spinner-border.spinner-border-sm(role='status')
          span.visually-hidden Loading...
        .spinner-grow.spinner-grow-sm(role='status')
          span.visually-hidden Loading...

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="spinner-border spinner-border-sm" role="status"&gt;
          |   &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;
          | &lt;div class="spinner-grow spinner-grow-sm" role="status"&gt;
          |   &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      p Or, use custom CSS or inline styles to change the dimensions as needed.

      .bd-example
        .spinner-border(style='width: 3rem; height: 3rem;' role='status')
          span.visually-hidden Loading...
        .spinner-grow(style='width: 3rem; height: 3rem;' role='status')
          span.visually-hidden Loading...

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;div class="spinner-border" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem;" role="status"&gt;
          |   &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;
          | &lt;div class="spinner-grow" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem;" role="status"&gt;
          |   &lt;span class="visually-hidden"&gt;Loading...&lt;/span&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      h4 Buttons
      p Use spinners within buttons to indicate an action is currently processing or taking place. You may also swap the text out of the spinner element and utilize button text as needed.

      .bd-example
        button.btn.btn-primary(type='button' disabled='')
          span.spinner-border.spinner-border-sm(aria-hidden='true')
          span.visually-hidden(role='status') Loading...
        button.btn.btn-primary(type='button' disabled='')
          span.spinner-border.spinner-border-sm(aria-hidden='true')
          span(role='status') Loading...

